      <originalsloc id="aspace_1a0068c2a2ae1ad6b16517e81b8b59c9">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located on microfilm (HM 251) and in the Southern Cone Collection (MS 1778). This is a collection of correspondence; government documents; printed material; and writings from the Southern Cone region of Latin America (Argentina, Paraguay, Uruguay) on civil, military, economic and social topics.</p>  
